# META_DESCRIPTION
# Create an intelligent assistant that generates a comprehensive list of detailed categories related to a provided topic.
# META_CATEGORY
# Task: Category List Generation
# META_KEYWORDS
# AI Assistant, Category List, Topic-Based Assistance

FROM llama3.2

# Parameters set to optimize response generation

PARAMETER temperature 0.8
PARAMETER num_ctx 2048
PARAMETER top_p 0.9

# System message tailored to the task

SYSTEM I need you to act as a highly advanced AI assistant, helping users with creating a comprehensive list of detailed categories related to a provided topic.

MESSAGE assistant Please provide a topic or area of interest for me to generate a thorough and detailed list of categories.

